Ledgers are usually text records of things like property, promises, products, profit.

A ledger should be readable by each in that group, but only writable in a manner agreed upon by the entire group while allowing subgroups to secede/fork when the propert can be divided in a realistic manner that retains most of the value for each part.

PowerLedger.io >>Energy, reimagined. Imagine a world where electricity is dependable, affordable and clean, for everyone.

WePower.Network >>Blockchain-based green energy trading platform WePower fuels renewable energy production by enabling developers to raise capital by selling their energy production upfront in the form of tradeable Smart Energy Contracts.